---
title: Pan-Seared Pork Chops with Apple Compote, Spinach, and Sautéed Onions
description: Apples and pork go together like peas and carrots – especially when we’re talking juicy, pan-seared chops and apple compote. For extra-crispy potatoes, place your baking sheet in the oven while the oven preheats!
